programme.title: Revenge
programme.desc: Richard tar med sin alskarinna Jen på lyxig jaktweekend med grabbarna. Efter en lång festnatt har hans ena kompis svårt att hålla fingrarna borta från Jen, och snart går allt overstyr. Skarrad efter våldtakten berattar Jen for en ointresserad Richard vad som hant. Hon hotar då med att beratta allt for hans fru, vilket istallet gor honom rasande och våldsam. Morbultad och blodig lamnar killarna Jen i oknen for att mota sitt ode, men hon ar inte redo att do. Hon ar redo for HÄMND!

programme.title: Get the Gringo
programme.desc: En amerikansk yrkesforbrytare tillfångatas av den mexikanska polisen nar han forsoker ta sig over gransen i en bil full med stulna pengar. Han blir ford till det okanda El Pueblito-fangelset som liknar en våldsam och hårdbevakad stad i staden. Trots att han lyckats hålla sin identitet hemlig blir han uppsokt av en korrumperad tjansteman från den amerikanska ambassaden som har vittring på pengarna. Men han ar inte den enda, aven det bestulna ganget ar honom på spåren. Amerikanens hopp att lyckas fly satts ovantat till en pojke vars ode kan vara nyckeln till friheten for dem båda.

programme.title: Raining in the Mountain
programme.desc: I ett buddhisttempel i Mingdynastins Kina ar det dags for abboten att utse sin eftertradare. Men bland kandidaterna finns det de som framst ar ute efter att stjala den ovarderliga skriften i templets skattkammare. Intriger och allianser uppstår nar personliga ambitioner och andliga stravanden kolliderar.

programme.title: Skurkar och banditer
programme.desc: Tony Roma (Tomas Milian) ar alla tiders halaste gigolo, en sol-och-vårare och skojare specialiserad på att knycka formogna hemmafruars diamanter. Till slut kopplas den hemliga polisen Parker (Bud Spencer) in for att ta fast den lille skojaren. Parker vill helst åka på semester med sin stora familj. Istallet tvingas han nu skydda Tony sedan denne blivit vittne till ett maffiamord. Sjalvklart haglar råsoparna och smockorna nar Parker tar sig an maffiaganget och kastar skurkarna rakt igenom dorrar och vaggar.

programme.title: Texas Red
programme.desc: Den sanna historien om legendariske Texas Red, en afroamerikansk man som vildsint jagades utmed prariens sargade landskap av hundratals laglosa cowboys genom Mississippis vintervildmark. Allt for att lagga beslag på den hogst eftertraktade beloningen.

programme.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles 3
programme.desc: Det hela borjar med att en magisk spira transporterar deras goda van April genom tid och rum, anda till samurajernas Japan. Leonardo och ganget ger sig genast av efter henne, och måste nu besegra den elake Lord Naringa for att radda den insparrade April och återta spiran som lorden kommit over. Annars lar de bli fast i medeltida Japan i eviga tider. Och dar finns ju inte ens några pizzerior…

programme.title: Fungi
programme.desc: En svamporganism har slagit ut storre delen av jordens befolkning. I en bunker någonstans i Sverige har ett forskarteam isolerat sig och kampar for att hitta ett botemedel. 19-åriga Leah forsoker anpassa sig till denna instangda tillvaro med sin pappa, militaren Gustav. Forskarduon Vera och Kim ser hoppet om en battre framtid hotas nar bunkerns ventilationssystem går sonder. Teamet tvingas ut på en farlig resa och det visar sig snart att svamporganismen inte ar det enda livsfarliga hotet i varlden utanfor.

programme.title: Udda eller jamt
programme.desc: Polisen har misslyckats med att krossa ligan som svarar for den illegala spelverksamheten i Florida. Marinofficeren Johnny Firpo (Terence Hill) tar over uppdraget och raknar med hjalp av ex-spelaren Charlie Firpo (Bud Spencer). Det udda paret visar sig vara halvbroder, men Charlie vill andå inte hjalpa Johnny. Inte forran denne ljuger ihop en historia om att deras far ar blind och måste genomgå en dyr operation. Charlie inser att han måste tjana ihop till operationen genom ett antal poker- och spelvinster. Som vanligt får paret också många tillfallen att utnyttja sina stenhårda navar!

programme.title: Salt And Fire
programme.desc: En forskare blir kidnappad och slangd ut i en dodsbringande oken dar hon måste kampa mot elementen for att overleva.

programme.title: Cold Zone
programme.desc: En storm ar på vag. Ingen kan forutsaga den. Ingen kan mata dess storlek. Nu måste en familj overleva den. Och ingen kan soka skydd från stormen, ingen kommer in från kylan…

programme.title: Flight World War II
programme.desc: Fångad I en strid mellan Tyska och Allierade styrkor kampar passagerarna i en modern 757 jet for att overleva efter att deras gjort en tidsresa tillbaka till 1940. I deras stravan att overleva lyckas de påverka historien och utgången av Andra Varldskriget.

programme.title: Impact Earth
programme.desc: En astronomiprofessor som jobbat for NASA inser att en destruktiv asteroid ar på kollisionskurs med jorden och måste få sin familj i sakerhet samtidigt som han varnar varlden for denna hotande forodelse.

programme.title: Jungle
programme.desc: Den unge, israeliske Yossi Ghinsberg lamnar en trygg framtid bakom sig for folja en osannolik drom som for honom in i Amazonas regnskogs mystiska djup.. Under ett års tid gor han en resa som många innan honom har gjort men nar han blir bekant med två andra aventyrare, Kevin Gale och Marcus Stamm och de tre moter den morka och karismatiske Karl Ruchprecter foljer de med honom in i djungeln. Vad som borjar som forverkligandet av en drom forvandlas snart till ett hemskt och psykologiskt test av fortroende och mod. Den sanna historien om att overleva mot alla odds, baserad på Yossi Ghinsbergs memoarer.

programme.title: Saknad i strid (Missing in Action)
programme.desc: Amerikanska soldater hålls fångna i Vietnam — och det ar upp till en man att fora hem dem i denna fartfyllda action/aventyrsfilm med kampsportslegenden Chuck Norris. Efter en djarv flykt från ett krigsfånglager ar overste James Braddock (Norris) på ett uppdrag att lokalisera och radda saknade soldater med hjalp av en tjansteman från utrikesdepartementet (Lenore Kasdorf) och en tidigare armekompis (M. Emmet Walsh). Denna enmansarme ar redo att ta sig in i Vietnam… men kan han ta sig ut igen?

programme.title: Gun
programme.desc: Vapenrelaterat våld och en skenande brottsstatistik får polisen i Detroit att tillsammans med FBI starta ett fullskaligt krig mot stadens vapensmugglare. Rich och hans organisation blir de framsta måltavlorna for operationen. Och då Rich, hans baste van Angel, och hans alskarinna och leverantor Gabriella råkar ut for en affarsuppgorelse som går fel, avslojas en stor hemlighet som skakar Rich anda in i margen. Det blir hogexplosiv action med bland annat Val Kilmer, Curtis ”50 Cent” Jackson och Danny Trejo!

programme.title: Skumma polare
programme.desc: Trinityseriens stjarna Bud Spencer återvander till vilda vastern i regissoren Michele Lupo’s komedi om bedragaren Buddy, som misstas for en lakare efter att hans van Cocoa oavsiktligt stjal en resvaska med kirurgiska instrument. Buddy bosatter sig i den lilla staden som en experimentell lakare. Nar ett gang våldsamma brottslingar forsoker ta over staden, visar det sig att hans sanna talang ar att slå ner skurkar synkad till musik som humoristiskt komponerats av spaghettivastmastaren Ennio Morricone.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: Cold Zone
programme.desc: En storm ar på vag. Ingen kan forutsaga den. Ingen kan mata dess storlek. Nu måste en familj overleva den. Och ingen kan soka skydd från stormen, ingen kommer in från kylan…

programme.title: Joyride
programme.desc: Jon ar en forkrossad men andå charmig odugling i nastan allt han foretar sig, Luke ar en mastare på att kora bil och på flykt från sitt forflutna och Keira ar drive-thru-bitrade på ett burgerstalle och veganaktivist. Tillsammans bildar de tre en trio tillfalliga banditer nar de reser genom hela Nya Zeeland i en "lånad" gul Mini Cooper och ifrågasatter samhallets likriktning och jagar forlorad karlek med ett massivt polisuppbåd och varsta mediacirkusen hack i hal.

programme.title: Banana Joe
programme.desc: Den italienska westernstjarnan Bud Spencer (hans riktiga namn ar Carlo Pedersoli) spelar en godhjartad men jarnnavad bananodlare som bor i en liten djungelby. Ett stort bananforetag vill exploatera byn, och nar Joe satter sig på tvaren bestammer sig foretagsledaren – en gangster – att satta dit honom. Resultatet ar ett komiskt aventyr med många energiska slagsmål.

programme.title: Man On A Ledge (2012)
programme.desc: Vågar du ta nasta steg? Den forrymde fången Nick Cassidy står plotsligt hogt upp på en avsats på en skyskrapa i New York. Kommer han att hoppa? På nolltid har Nick fångat hela stadens och alla mediers uppmarksamhet. Och medan alla tittar upp, ser ingen den utstuderade kupp som ager rum på andra sidan gatan. Hanger dessa båda handelser ihop? Kommer polispsykologen Lydia sanningen på spåren? Och har Nick i sjalva verket en helt annan agenda?

programme.title: Legal Action
programme.desc: Stjarnadvokaten Casey McKay lockas till en liten stad av sin exfru for att forsvara hennes bror som står åtalad for att ha mordat en distriktsåklagare. Casey blottlagger en konspirationsharva som staller honom oga mot oga med mr Gates, stadens allra mest korrupte markexploator. En f.d. marinsoldat hjalper Casey i konflikten nar det står klart att han behover mer an sitt juridiska kunnande for att hålla sig vid liv och radda sin klient.

programme.title: Triassic Hunt
programme.desc: Nar två genetiskt framtagna dinousarer rymmer från laboratoriet kallas en styrka legosoldater in for att fånga dem. Men nar soldaterna inser att dinousarerna ar lika smarta som manniskor borjar en katt och råttalek utan dess like.

programme.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles 3
programme.desc: Det hela borjar med att en magisk spira transporterar deras goda van April genom tid och rum, anda till samurajernas Japan. Leonardo och ganget ger sig genast av efter henne, och måste nu besegra den elake Lord Naringa for att radda den insparrade April och återta spiran som lorden kommit over. Annars lar de bli fast i medeltida Japan i eviga tider. Och dar finns ju inte ens några pizzerior…

programme.title: Shockwave
programme.desc: Nar en massiv vulkanisk storm drabbar varlden forsoker geofysikern Kate Ferris overtyga forsvarsdepartementet att det inte ar ett naturligt fenomen. Det ar resultatet av ett seismiskt supervapen, kant som Hell Storm, som aktiverats. Kate måste komma på ett satt att stoppa chockvågen innan den hotar manskligheten.

programme.title: Skurkar och banditer
programme.desc: Tony Roma (Tomas Milian) ar alla tiders halaste gigolo, en sol-och-vårare och skojare specialiserad på att knycka formogna hemmafruars diamanter. Till slut kopplas den hemliga polisen Parker (Bud Spencer) in for att ta fast den lille skojaren. Parker vill helst åka på semester med sin stora familj. Istallet tvingas han nu skydda Tony sedan denne blivit vittne till ett maffiamord. Sjalvklart haglar råsoparna och smockorna nar Parker tar sig an maffiaganget och kastar skurkarna rakt igenom dorrar och vaggar.

programme.title: Awake
programme.desc: En man vaknar på sjukhuset utan att minnas vem han ar och hur han har hamnat dar. Hans sjukskoterska (Eastwood) hittar ingen legitimation på honom och kallar honom bara John Doe (Rhys Meyers). Polisen brakar in på sjukhuset och anklagar John for att vara en seriemordare som har dodat flera unga kvinnor i trakten. Nar John ska foras till forhor lyckas han fly med hjalp av Diana, som ar saker på att han ar oskyldig. De kor till den senaste brottsplatsen for att hitta ledtrådar och svar som kan rentvå John från misstankarna. Den snalla sjukskoterskan tar reda på den skakande sanningen om Johns identitet och det nat av logner och svek som slutar i en sista kamp om hans overlevnad.

programme.title: The Villainess
programme.desc: Yrkesmordaren Sook-hee tar hamnd på de man som dodade hennes make. Efter att ha forlorat medvetandet vaknar hon upp hos den nationella sakerhetstjansten som vill att hon ska ta an sig topphemliga uppdrag. Sook-hee bestammer sig for att acceptera sin nya identitet som Yeon-soo for att hålla sig vid liv. Hon moter Hyun-soo och de borjar dromma om att starta en familj. Men på deras brollopsdag blir hon tilldelad ett uppdrag som kommer att forandra allt.

programme.title: Saints and Soldiers
programme.desc: I mitten av december 1944 rycker Hitlers arme fram genom Ardennesskogen in i Belgien. Furir Nathan Greer och hans nara van Gordon Gunderson blir liksom hundratals andra amerikanska soldater tillfångatagna av nazisterna mitt ute på ett kallt och snotackt falt. Allt eftersom utbryter panik och forvirring nar de tyska soldaterna borjar skjuta de amerikanska fångarna. Greer, Gunderson och en handfull andra soldater lyckas fly undan tyskarna. Utan varken vapen eller mat går de en hård och kall vinter till motes i hopp om att hitta tillbaka till det område dar de allierade befinner sig. En lång och mycket farlig vandring borjar.

programme.title: Revenge
programme.desc: Richard tar med sin alskarinna Jen på lyxig jaktweekend med grabbarna. Efter en lång festnatt har hans ena kompis svårt att hålla fingrarna borta från Jen, och snart går allt overstyr. Skarrad efter våldtakten berattar Jen for en ointresserad Richard vad som hant. Hon hotar då med att beratta allt for hans fru, vilket istallet gor honom rasande och våldsam. Morbultad och blodig lamnar killarna Jen i oknen for att mota sitt ode, men hon ar inte redo att do. Hon ar redo for HÄMND!

programme.title: Raising Wildlife
programme.desc: Raising wildlife can be a long-term commitment: elephant calves are dependent on their mothers for three years and chimpanzees rely on special attention for about seven. In this episode, we visit the Lilayi Elephant Nursery in Zambia and the Mefou Primate Park in Cameroon to meet the highly committed people who take on this responsibility. Night or day, a baby elephant can never be left alone and many of the chimpanzee orphans arrive highly traumatised. Their care givers need to work very hard to restore their trust and will to live. At the Kwaggasvlaktes Wildlife Centre in South Africa some baby Wildebeest rely on heart-warming help from humans and an unusual sheep to survive.

programme.title: Wild Bavaria
programme.desc: The moon disappears behind the horizon and the stage is set for a new day in the Alps of Berchtesgaden.

programme.title: Wild Bavaria
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Wild Bavaria - In The Shadow of the Watzmann.
programme.desc: Mighty and mysterious, King Watzmann sits above Germanys only alpine national park.

programme.title: Wild Baltic
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Wild Baltic - Life on the Amber Coast
programme.desc: The first episode of this two-part nature documentary presents the natural beauty of the shifting sand dunes of the Curonian Spit, the romantic beaches of the Latvian Baltic Sea and the island worlds of Estonia. Time and again, this deserted and almost untouched nature fascinates. In the winter, ringed seals give birth to their young on the pack ice. In the spring, Konik wild horse stallions fight fierce battles amongst themselves, while colourful European rollers fly through the dune forests. Lynxes wander through the coastal forests and in the orchid meadows turncoats and hoopoes find more than enough food. On the islands around Saaremaa in Estonia, grey seals hunt for fish. They share...

programme.title: Wild Baltic
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Wild Baltic - Enchanted Forests and Moors
programme.desc: The wide, often untouched wilderness of the Baltic hinterland is home to many animals. More than 35 brown bears live in the primeval forests of Alutaguse. In the spring, the Soomaa National Park transforms into a huge lake. Europes widest waterfall is located in Latvia. In the beginning of May, vimba bream follow the course of the River Venta. The hardly 5-centimetre-long fish have to overcome a 4-metre-long rock barrier in order to reach their spawning grounds.

programme.title: The Moor
programme.desc: Moors and peatlands are oases in the cultivated landscape of Central Europe.

programme.title: Bosnia Herzegovina
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Bosnia and Herzegovina: The Abundant North
programme.desc: Wild and unknown lies the still undiscovered natural paradise of Bosnia and Herzegovina in the heart of Europe. Rough mountains, dense forests and wild waterfalls characterize the picture of the untouched landscapes. Lynx, wolves and bears roam mountains and valleys. One of the last primeval forests in Europe is a retreat for many endangered animal species. Bosnia and Herzegovina is actually an undiscovered natural paradise in the middle of Europe.

programme.title: Bosnia Herzegovina
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Bosnia and Herzegovina: The Karstic South
programme.desc: The barren, karstic south of the country, Herzegovina, also impresses with its natural landscapes. One of them is the Livno field. Not only is it the largest wetland in the country, it is also the largest regularly flooded karst field in the world. About 700 wild horses live in this unique landscape. Their ancestors were working horses that were abandoned here more than 50 years ago. Another special feature of the karst landscape are the rivers with their tufa barriers. The countless waterfalls that pour over it are a unique natural phenomenon.

programme.title: Portugals Nature Parks
programme.desc: The Parque Nacional Peneda-Geres is the only national park in Portugal. An area of almost 700 square kilometers, located in the extreme north of Portugal. Barren and rocky ridges in the plateaus, contrast with large forests and lush ground vegetation in deep valleys, crossed by lakes and rivers. The park is known for its oak forests, which are predominantly pedunculate and Pyrenean oaks. Among the typical animals of the park are the small Garrano ponies, a very old breed of horse and the only one in Europe that still lives in the wild.

programme.title: Portugals Nature Parks
programme.desc: The highest mountain range in Portugal is the Serra da Estrela. The episode embarks on a voyage of discovery to adventurous rock formations and villages steeped in tradition. The nature park is the largest protected area on the Iberian peninsula. In the mountain range we accompany the young scientist Ana Matos, who wants to breathe new life into old traditions, and cheese maker Maria Natália Lopes. She watches over more than 350 sheeps.

programme.title: Portugals Nature Parks
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 South West Portugal: Alentejano and Costa Vicentina
programme.desc: In the southwest of Portugal lies the little known Parque Natural do Sudoeste Alentejano e Costa Vicentina. It encompasses a narrow coastal strip that runs along the coast to the south of Portugal. Sparsely populated, this coastal region, which was placed under protection in 1988, is considered one of the last intact ecosystems in Europe. The steep cliffs, the almost constant wind and high waves have ensured that mass tourism has not gained a foothold here. There are still near-natural forests and a diverse bird life.

programme.title: Portugals Nature Parks
programme.desc: Madeira - Portugals autonomous island in the Atlantic Ocean, is closer to the African coast than to the mother country Portugal, from which it is separated by about 900 kilometers. The islands name comes from Portuguese sailors who claimed the uninhabited isle for themselves in 1419. Madeira means wood and that was available in abundance. Almost the entire surface was covered by dense forest. Since 1982, two-thirds of the landscape has been protected.

programme.title: Portugals Nature Parks
programme.desc: The "Parque Natural da Ria Formosa" is one of the largest lagoon conservation areas in Europe. Bordered by five natural islands. A mosaic of sandbanks, brackish and freshwater lagoons and salt marshes. In 2010, the "Ria Formosa" was chosen as one of the seven natural wonders of Portugal. It is a unique ecosystem: in the winter months, more than 20,000 birds gather here. In addition, the nature park has one of the largest seahorse populations internationally. More than half of all fish species in the Atlantic are said to spawn in the lagoon.

programme.title: Wilderness in Europe: The Bohemian Forest
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 The Psychogramm of a Spiritual Landscape
programme.desc: The Bohemian Forest is the source of the Vltava River, home to primeval forests, untouched high moors and bubbling torrents. This archaic stretch of land, which includes the Bavarian Forest, was long considered impenetrable and mysterious. Since the fall of the Iron Curtain, Bavarian border residents have rediscovered new references to this unusual forest landscape for themselves. This is also the case with photo artist Bastian Kalous, who has been documenting his homeland for years with nostalgic-looking Polaroid photographs and is dealing with its eventful history for an illustrated book. Or Elisa Belotti and Marco Heurich, who have dedicated their lives to the lynxes. In order for...

programme.title: Wilderness in Europe: The Bohemian Forest
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Boundary Experiences in Muhlviertel
programme.desc: Pavel Hubeny, whose life would be unthinkable without the forest, is the head of the Šumava National Park. He is committed to ensuring that a primeval forest can grow for future generations, in which man does not interfere. This vision of a primeval forest is also shared by the forester Claus Bassler, who wants to counteract the extinction of species by having trees felled to create artificial deadwood and thus a new habitat for rare beetles and fungi. On the Vltava River lies the small town of Krumlov, the "Pearl of the Bohemian Forest" with its Baroque theater and fully preserved stage technology from the 17th century. Here the director Zuzana Vrbová enchants people from all over the...

programme.title: The U.S. East Coast
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 The U.S. East Coast, The Heart of New England
programme.desc: From New York, the journey up the coast leads into the heart of New England. We visit Yale; spend some time in the 19th century mansions at Newport, RI; tour the coastal fishing and vacation towns of Massachusetts, and then meet a modern entrepreneur in Boston and see her rooftop gardens.

programme.title: The U.S. East Coast
programme.sub-title: S01 : E04 The U.S. East Coast, Surf And Turf
programme.desc: New Hampshire has only 19 kilometers of coastline and short summers, all the more reason Shauna Fraser takes every opportunity to be by the sea. In the sheltered harbor of Rye, Shauna also targets inner attitude with yoga on a paddleboard.

programme.title: The U.S. East Coast
programme.sub-title: S01 : E05 The U.S. East Coast, The Southern States
programme.desc: We travel from Georgia through the Carolinas to Virginia, ending near Washington, DC. Along the way we meet a Georgia farmer; talk to painter J. Chris Wilson in Charleston; sail along the Outer Banks of Carolina, and visit rural Virginia, experiencing life in the beautiful southern states.

programme.title: mareTV: Newfoundland - Canadas Eastern Point
programme.desc: In Newfoundland, at the easternmost tip of North America, the landscape is pristine, dramatic, and very sparsely populated. In summer, icebergs occasionally drift along the steep cliffs. When the "Titanic" collided with an iceberg and sank just 300 miles off the coast of Newfoundland in 1912, the last radio messages were picked up in a small wooden hut on the Avalon Peninsula. Today, most Newfoundlanders live on Avalon. There are particularly many seabirds here. In Witless Bay, the newborn puffins are ready for their first descent into the Atlantic. But some stray onto the coastal road, attracted by the lights of the hotels and restaurants. In doing so, they run the risk of being run...

programme.title: mareTV: In Alaskas Fjord World
programme.desc: Gigantic fjords and over 5,000 small islands: In Alaskas south theres a lot of wilderness and little civilization. The region between the capital Juneau and the Canadian border is also known by locals as the "Last Frontier", the last outpost. Michelle Masden, for example, has come to terms with the harsh conditions here. She is the only seaplane pilot in the region. She earns her living with her 65-year-old Beaver: as an air taxi, transport plane and now and then as a rescuer in last necessity. Michelle flies anything and everything: spare parts and food, doctors, hikers and hunters. For the fishermen of southern Alaska she searches for large shoals of fish and guides the captains to...

programme.title: mareTV: The Caribbean for explorers: St. Vincent and the Grenadines
programme.desc: Much more Caribbean than on the islands of St. Vincent and the Grenadines is hardly possible. Deserted beaches, uninhabited islands, lush vegetation, the 33 islands in total are dreamlike with extremely hospitable inhabitants. Miranda Phillips runs a laundry and water boat on Bequia. Every morning, the 32-year-old navigates from yacht to yacht with her small bright green service vehicle and is already expected by most skippers. Miranda promises radiantly fresh laundry, which she delivers again the same day. And so there is always something going on in her tiny laundrette in the harbour. It turns into a karaoke bar in the evening, because that is Mirandas great passion. Eban Olliver has...

programme.title: mareTV: Peru - Coast of the Incas
programme.desc: Dramatically, the coast plunges into the sea, the so-called Costa of Peru is a gigantic desert on the Pacific Ocean, 2,400 kilometers long. Rugged, bizarre, like from another star. Ancient cultures settled here, the Moche and the Chimú. Later the proud Inca, the self-proclaimed royal people of the Andes, ruled. In the small town of Huanchaco in northern Peru, the fishermen build a new boat every month: from reed. The small ships are called Caballito de Totora (reed horses), because the shape is reminiscent of a horse and the fishermen ride in it kneeling in the waves. About 2,000 years ago, the moche used it to go out to sea. Carlos Segura Azola is a descendant of the moche. He is...

programme.title: Cuba - Brilliantly Caribbean
programme.desc: Even anyone who has not yet been to Cuba can conjure up certain images of American vintage street cruisers, imposing buildings that have seen better days, white sandy beaches full of palms and loving couples on the Malecon against a backdrop of crashing waves. This island is somewhat of a myth and its people generate a special joie de vivre. The legendary Hershey Train departs for Matanzas from the capital, Havana. On the oldest electrified railway line in the Caribbean, 60-year-old Spanish carriages make their way along al-most 100 kilometres of coastline in the most relaxed way possible. The Salvavidas on Varadero, probably the most famous beach on the island, have a particular-ly...

programme.title: Caribbean sisters: The Lesser Antilles St. Kitts and Nevis
programme.desc: In the centre of the Caribbean, volcanoes rise steeply from the sea, thus shaping the sister islands of St. Kitts and Nevis. Their slopes, covered in lush rainforests, snow-white, sandy beaches and the surrounding tur-quoise tinted waters provide the ultimate setting for this record-breaking, albeit tiny island paradise: Both islets are the smallest of the Caribbean dwarf states and also rank among the world’s ten smallest states. A hot pepper sauce, made of a creative mixture of ginger, garlic, thyme and extraordinarily hot chillies that thrive in the hot and humid climate of Nevis, is simmering on the stove of Violet and Llewellyn’s house. Lemmy Pemberton digs up abandoned turtle nests...

programme.title: mareTV: Mexicos Caribbean Coast
programme.desc: The palm tree laden beaches on Mexicos Riviera Maya on the Yucatan peninsula are endless, and the turquoise sea with its gentle Caribbean surf is a warm 25 degrees during the mild winter in this part of the world. Between Cancún and Punta Allen, where once there was little more than bushland and a few sleepy fishing villages, vibrant life has evolved during the past three decades. Richard Sowa has lived on a floating island for the past 15 years: an island he built himself out of empty plastic bottles. The bon vivant him-self sees it as a "solution for our planets refuse problem". Off Punta Allen, a village in the bay of Sian Kaan, Mexican Mara Coral Ley and her cousin Kim, continue to...

programme.title: mareTV: Curacao, Blue Wonder of the Caribbean
programme.desc: Curacao is one of the most popular attractions for countless cruise ships on their trips through the Caribbean, because it is located outside of the hurricane belt. This is why Eric Miguel is constantly in action. He is the bridge keeper of the Queen Emma Bridge, the landmark of Curacaos capital, Willemstad. After his shift, Eric goes to Yvonne Troemans cook-shop. Her speciality is Kadushi, a cactus soup. The ingredients include cactus flesh, pigtails, mussels and a few secret "treats". Barbara van Bebber is the only submarine pilot on Curacao and literally gets to the bottom of things amidst the turquoise-blue wonder of the Caribbean. She charters out her sub to marine biologists and...

programme.title: mareTV: Martinique
programme.desc: The island of Martinique is a piece of France in the Caribbean, between Florida and South America. And of course, Savoir-vivre applies just as it does on the other side of the Atlantic, between the English Channel and the Mediterranean. Jacky Pascault is the first and only man to cultivate mushrooms in the Caribbean. Everywhere else, they grow on artificially fertilised soil, but Jackys Champignons Tropicaux flourish on sugar cane fibres. Nicole Vilo tailors hats and dresses out of coconut palms. Of course, the catwalk for the models wearing her first collection is one of the countless dream beaches. The Martiniquais sail on boats they call Yole, which have no keel and are therefore...

programme.title: The U.S. East Coast
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 The U.S. East Coast, The City and the Sea
programme.desc: The journey up the coast continues through Delaware to suburban New Jersey, and onwards into the heart of Manhattan. In Delaware, famous as a corporate tax haven, we visit a winery. In New York City we zip around with a bicycle courier and then head out to Long Island for oysters.

programme.title: The U.S. East Coast
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 The U.S. East Coast, Florida - The Sunshine State
programme.desc: Nowhere is the American way of life as relaxed as on Floridas beaches. The Keys, a chain of islands at the far southern end of the state, reveal a more laid-back side of the USA. But all of Florida amazes -- with secluded beaches, unspoiled nature, and the legacy of the early European settlers.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: A Night of Horror at Devils Plateau (Marie-Jeanne Meyer Case) - On June 18, 2011, Marie-Jeanne Meyer, 17-years old, waved goodbye to her little sister before leaving for her daily jog on the heights of Tournon in Ardèche. She never came back. Three days later, her mutilated body was found in a freshly dug pit, near an area known to be cursed, "The Devils Plateau." Whats more, the crime scene looked like a mystical ritual ... Was it a ritual murder? Revenge? An unfortunate encounter? ...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: A Mysterious Murder at the Farm (Valerie Bary Case)- On Friday, March 26, 2004, in the region of Dijon, Laurent Bary came home from his work to discover the lifeless body of his wife, Valerie, bathing in a pool of blood. According to the investigators initial findings, the 38-year-old nurses aid had been stabbed several times, seeming to validate the theory of a robbery gone wrong.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: On July 13, 2011, two boaters retrieved a suitcase that was floating in the bay of Lorient. Inside, they discovered the tied up corpse of a man.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Bloody Christmas next to the Leman lake (CASE OF RUTH LÉGERET) - On January 4, 2006, Ruth Legeret was found dead in the middle of a pool of blood at her luxurious property in Vevey, Switzerland. Next to her was the lifeless body of her friend, Marina Studer. Who could have killed these two simple and wealthy widows? Clue after clue, the Swiss polices investigation would revolve around an environment of family jealousy and financial greed.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: September 16 2005. The lifeless body of Audrey Jouannet, 24, is found hidden under the bed in her small apartment in Soisy-sur-Seine. It soon becomes apparent that the young woman has been tortured at length before being strangled. But surprisingly, though the highly meticulous murderer has taken care to leave no sign of his passage, the autopsy reveals traces of sperm on the victim. It will take all of the investigators intuition to pierce the mystery of this heinous crime...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Sylvain Dromard finds the body of his wife Laurence lying in a pool of blood in the kitchen. The crime was particularly violent and the theory of a burglary that went wrong is soon excluded. But investigators dont understand who could want the adorable hairdresser of Saint-Martin-dAblois dead. During the investigation, the work of profilers will enable them to draw a very precise portrait of the murderer...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: After an ordinary dinner, Pierre and Gabrielle Labrell suffer severe abdominal pains.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Nelly Cremel, 39, leaves her home to go jogging... never to return. Eight days later, after a vast search campaign, her body is found. Theres no doubt that its murder. The case soon ignites public opinion, even inflaming passions at the highest level of the state. The clues lead investigators on a number of trails, from the shadows of the French secret service to a manhunt for a possible sex maniac, in a case of murder most foul.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Willy Pomonti, a retired architect, is found savagely murdered in his opulent villa in La Celle-Saint-Cloud, near Paris. It soon becomes clear that the man has been tortured prior to death. At several points during this extraordinary enquiry, police will feel theyre holding the culprit... It will take them ten years to finally shed light on this particularly violent crime.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: The lifeless body of Christophe Lejard is found by his son just metres from their home. The man was shot in the head as he was getting into his car to go to work. A veritable execution, which at first glance doesnt square with the profile of the quiet family man. Yet behind the appearances, the investigation gradually reveals all the hate and resentment that revolved around the victim.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: A man walks into a gendarmerie near Saint-Malo to report that his wife has been missing since the previous day. The couple are going through a divorce, but this mother would never have left her seven children alone! An extensive search is undertaken but the woman cannot be found. What has happened to Adeline Piet? The investigation spans several years and experiences many twists.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: The corpse of Priscillia Ciatti, 14, is discovered by the side of a field, a few hundred metres from her family home. The teenager has been stabbed sixty times with a knife and -an extra sordid detail - a devil mask is found next to her body. Was Priscillia the victim of a prowler? A serial killer? A maniac inspired by a horror movie? Investigators soon find that the young girl felt she was being watched, and even threatened...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: In the early hours of the morning, Mathilde Croguennec, 18, attending "Teknival" in Brittany, is found at the foot of a tree with her throat cut. Investigators face the task of finding the killer from among the 43,000 participants of this huge open-air festival of electronic music, where drink and drugs are consumed in abundance. An unusual investigation that leads the police down a number of false avenues.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Arriving at her work, the secretary of a small firm in the suburbs of Geneva finds the body of Jean-Raymond Blatti, the companys new accountant. The man is lying in a pool of blood and, on his belly, the murderer has written "DIRTY RAPIST". Yet Jean-Raymond Blatti was never charged with sexual assault. Over the course of the investigation, this inscription will appear as one of the many mysteries of this case which is particularly rich in twists and turns.

programme.title: Auggie
programme.desc: Felix Greystone har en bit kvar till pensionsåldern, men foretaget pressar honom att gå i fortidspension. I avskedsgåva får han ett par smartglasogon, som vacker anvandarens storsta drommar till liv. Nar Felix frus karriar tar fart och dottern borjar bli sjalvstandig inser Felix hur ensam han kanner sig. For att fly den plågsamma ensamheten fordjupar Felix sig allt mer i sina smartglasogons varld, vilket påfrestar Felix relation till familjen ytterligare.

programme.title: Evil Stepmom
programme.desc: Ett tvillingpar vill hjalpa sin pappa att borja dejta igen och skapar en profil på en dejtingsajt åt honom. Det drojer inte lange forran han får svar. En av tvillingflickorna blir van med pappans dejts dotter. Snart inser hon att det ar något som inte stammer. Men hur ska hon få sin nyforalskade pappa att inse allvaret?
En ung forfattare tvingas att acceptera sin dodlighet nar han diagnoseras med en sallsynt form av cancer. Med hjalp av sin basta van och en ung terapeut finner han modet att mota sjukdomen.

programme.title: From Time to Time
programme.desc: En spokhistoria som spanner over två varldar med mer an ett sekel från varandra. Nar 13-åriga Tolly upptacker att han på ett mystiskt satt kan resa mellan de två, borjar han ett aventyr som avslojar familjehemligheter som har begravts i generationer.

programme.title: Brain On Fire
programme.desc: Susannah Cahalan har nyligen avslutat sina universitetsstudier och lever dromlivet i New York. Hon ar en lovande journalist på New York Post och foralskad i musikern Stephen. Hennes chef ger henne det stora uppdraget som ska rivstarta hennes karriar och livet kan inte bli battre. Snart borjar saker och ting gå fel. Susannah drabbas av en influensa som inte vill ge sig, hon glommer saker och missar deadlines på jobbet. Hon hor att folk pratar om henne, ar overtygad om att Stephen har en annan flickvan och hon kan inte kontrollera sin kropp. Det blir snart varre; Susannah borjar få våldsamma anfall och hennes alltmer psykotiska upptradande innebar att hon standigt måste overvakas.

programme.title: Shattered Glass
programme.desc: Hayden Christensen spelar huvudrollen i denna kritikerrosade berattelse om en utskamd journalist, regisserad och samskriven av Billy Ray, Oscar®-nominerad forfattare av KAPTEN PHILLIPS. Nar den beromda journalisten Stephen Glass (Christensen) plotsligt utredas av en Forbes.com-reporter (Steve Zahn) avslojar sokandet att Glass har diktat ihop många av sina sensationella berattelser, vilket leder till hans ultimata fall i detta gripande, faktabaserade drama.

programme.title: Griffin and Phoenix
programme.desc: Nar Griffin har fått diagnosen att han har dodlig cancer bestammer han sig for att ta livet i egna hander och ha lite kul innan han dor. Samtidigt som tiden for hans liv rinner ut traffar han och blir kar i Phoenix - som också har en hemlighet.

programme.title: Equals
programme.desc: I en utopisk varld, dar våld och brott i princip ar utplånade via genetisk eliminering av kanslor, lever personer som Nia och Silas ett lugnt, handelselost och dronarlikt liv. De arbetar med att producera informationsmaterial på ett stort kontor och utvaxlar enbart artighetsfraser. Livet ar enkelt, anda till dess att ett rykte borjar florera: en sjukdom som orsakar att manniskor visar kanslor har brutit ut. Om det upptacks av overheten skickas de infekterade ivag, for att aldrig återvanda. Silas misstanker att han bar på sjukdomen och nar det bekraftas, blir han en paria. Trots det dras han till Nia, som också ar infekterad men har lyckats dolja symptomen battre an han sjalv.

programme.title: Candy
programme.desc: Heath Ledger ar den hoppfulla poeten Dan som hals over huvud foralskar sig i konstnaren Candy (Abbie Cornish). Dan ar heroinmissbrukare, men Candy ar fascinerad och dras till honom. Tillsammans beger de sig ut på ostadig mark, sammanbundna av deras vansinniga karlek och glupska sexuella aptit. Med hjalp av universitetsprofessorn Casper (Geoffrey Rush), som kan skaffa dem pengar och få gratis droger, inleder de båda bohemerna en farlig flort med doden.

programme.title: Undergods
programme.desc: En sci-fi-dystopi kryddad med svart humor om en varld med endast ett fåtal overlevande, som alla ar en aning trasiga på sitt satt. Den kafkaliknande miljon kombinerad med 2020-talets krossade drommar ger redan i sig tittaren gåshud. Filmen borjar med att två liksamlare går runt langs de odelagda gatorna och vid sidan av arbetet berattar om sina grusade drommar som drivit dem till det dystra nulaget.

programme.title: The Architect
programme.desc: En arkitekt hamnar i konflikt med en aktivist som bor i ett farligt komplex som arkitekten ritade.

programme.title: Journeyman
programme.desc: Efter att ha vunnit en tuff titelmatch på poang, kollapsar mellanviktsmastaren Matty Burton. Resan for att få tillbaka minnet och formågan att tala och rora sig blir hans tuffaste match någonsin och priset kan bli skyhogt då relationen till frun Emma och dottern Mia står på spel.

programme.title: Proxima
programme.desc: Sarah ar en fransk astronaut, och den enda kvinnliga deltagaren i det rymdprogram som forbereder sig infor en ett år lång expedition. Som ensamstående mamma till en åttaåring kanns expeditionen an mer kravande, och med lika delar skuld och mod forsoker hon hitta balans i sin roll som banbrytare och mamma.

programme.title: Evil Stepmom
programme.desc: Ett tvillingpar vill hjalpa sin pappa att borja dejta igen och skapar en profil på en dejtingsajt åt honom. Det drojer inte lange forran han får svar. En av tvillingflickorna blir van med pappans dejts dotter. Snart inser hon att det ar något som inte stammer. Men hur ska hon få sin nyforalskade pappa att inse allvaret?

programme.title: Griffin and Phoenix
programme.desc: Nar Griffin har fått diagnosen att han har dodlig cancer bestammer han sig for att ta livet i egna hander och ha lite kul innan han dor. Samtidigt som tiden for hans liv rinner ut traffar han och blir kar i Phoenix - som också har en hemlighet.

programme.title: Shattered Glass
programme.desc: Hayden Christensen spelar huvudrollen i denna kritikerrosade berattelse om en utskamd journalist, regisserad och samskriven av Billy Ray, Oscar®-nominerad forfattare av KAPTEN PHILLIPS. Nar den beromda journalisten Stephen Glass (Christensen) plotsligt utredas av en Forbes.com-reporter (Steve Zahn) avslojar sokandet att Glass har diktat ihop många av sina sensationella berattelser, vilket leder till hans ultimata fall i detta gripande, faktabaserade drama.

programme.title: Dinner Rush
programme.desc: Dinner Rush utspelar sig under vad som från borjan inte tycks vara något annat an en helt vanlig jaktig kvall på Louis Cropas (Danny Aiello) populara restaurang Gigino i det fashionabla TriBeCa-kvarteret i New York. En gång var trattorian en enkel familjerestaurang men nu har den forvandlats till kvarterets mesta innekrog, stallet dar alla vill bli sedda. Detta mycket tack vare krogaren Cropas son Udos (Edoardo Ballerini) innovativa matlagningskonst som kommit att bli stallets kannetecken. Och just den har kvallen ar restaurangen som ett kalejdoskop av livet i dagens New York...
En ung forfattare tvingas att acceptera sin dodlighet nar han diagnoseras med en sallsynt form av cancer. Med hjalp av sin basta van och en ung terapeut finner han modet att mota sjukdomen.

programme.title: Bekas
programme.desc: Tidigt 90-tal, Saddam Husseins regim har satt stor press på den kurdiska delen av Irak. Två hemlosa kurdiska pojkar ser Superman på stadens forsta biograf och bestammer sig for att ta sig till Amerika. For att komma dit behover de pass, pengar och en hel del tur. Tyvarr har de inget av detta men de borjar andå resan som ska ta dem mot drommen om Amerika.

programme.title: Mazes and Monsters
programme.desc: Robbie och hans collegekompisar ar alla besatta av rollspelet "Mazes and Monsters". Men spelen tar en marklig vandning nar Robbie borjar få visioner efter att de spelat en session på ett mystiskt, lokalt landmarke.

programme.title: Sommarminnen
programme.desc: Helène ar familjens matriark, och har agnat sitt liv åt att samla konst och antikviteter. Nar hennes liv till slut kommer till anda står hennes tre barn med ett stort arv i form av ett vackert gammalt lantgods och allt det huserar, men de ar allt annat an overens om hur dessa slaktklenoder ska forvaltas. Sommarminnen ar Guldpalmsvinnaren Olivier Assayas starka familjedrama med Juliette Binoche, Charles Berling och Jeremie Renier.

programme.title: Suicide Kings
programme.desc: Avery ar desperat: hans syster ar kidnappad och losensumman ar 2 miljoner dollar, och hans pappa har inte pengarna. Så Avery och hans polare kokar ihop en tuff, halvt sjalvmordsbenagen plan: att rova bort den pensionerade maffiabossen Charlie Bartolucci och tvinga honom att hitta flickan.

programme.title: Camp X-Ray
programme.desc: Kristen Stewart spelar huvudrollen i Peter Sattlers hyllade debutfilm Camp X-Ray. Hon spelar Amy Cole, en ung kvinna som tar varvning i amerikanska militaren i tron att hon kommer att skickas till Irak eller Afghanistan. Istallet blir hon stationerad som vakt på ett okant militarfangelse, med tuffa villkor for såval basens fångar som de få kvinnliga militarer som arbetar dar.

programme.title: Amores Perros
programme.desc: Karlek ar många saker — vissa bra, andra dåliga — men framfor allt suger den. En fruktansvard bilolycka binder samman tre berattelser, var och en med karaktarer som hanterar forlust, ånger och livets hårda verkligheter, allt i karlekens namn.

programme.title: En perfekt jullista

programme.title: Julens 12 Hundar
programme.desc: En arbetslos far skickar motvilligt sin dotter till sin moster- i en stad som forbjuder hundar. På vag till skolan en dag hittar hon en valp och behåller den- trots att hundfångaren ar i narheten. Nu måste hon gå till botten med vad som hander med alla hundar- och charma borgmastaren med den mest minnesvarda julforestallningen- staden någonsin har sett.

programme.title: Puppy Star Christmas
programme.desc: Pup Star-familjen har utokats! De nya valparna ar: Cindy, Rosie, Charlie, och Brody, som måste lara sig julens innebord. Nar Pup Stars elakingar forsoker forstora julen hamnar valparna på Nordpolen for att radda tomten och julstamningen. Deras aventyr ar fyllt av valp-tastiska sånger som sprider julgladje året om.

programme.title: Vilken tomte?

programme.title: Another Christmas Coincedence
programme.desc: Alice och Jack, två framlingar med totalt olika bakgrunder hamnar av en slump en helg på samma brollop. Det klickar direkt mellan dem men Alice ar tveksam till en ny relation efter ett havererat långdistansforhållande. Uppmuntrad av mamma Olga borjar Alice sakta vanja sig med tanken och borja dejta igen. Mer tillfalligheterna for dem narmare samtidigt som nya hinder avloser varann och utmanar den nyfunna romansen.

programme.title: A Winter Princess
programme.desc: Efter en prestigefull gala bestammer sig prinsessan Carly for att ta ett sabbatsår och hoppa på ett for henne dromjobb vid en skidanlaggning. Ingen av hennes nya arbetskamrater kanner till hennes ratta identitet, men nar medlemmar från den kungliga slakten borjar dyka upp vid anlaggningen blir det plotsligt valdigt komplicerat att hålla på hemligheten utan att bli upptackt. Allt medan de preppar for ett 50års jubileum av anlaggningen, och Carly som borjar bli stortkar i agarens bror Jesse. Carly står nu infor stora vagval i livet och kanner sig bara alltmer forvirrad ju langre tiden går…

programme.title: A Christmas Coincedence

En serie tillfalligheter for dem narmare varann. Ett ovader sveper over bygden som tvingar Paula att stanna over natten, och snart kommer hon inse att just de ar menade for varann…

Tragedy, resilience, and survival collide on the frontier.

programme.desc: Victims of oppressive town boss Honey are offered help by an unusual alliance of gunmen and circus performers.

programme.title: Fat Brothers of Trinity
programme.desc: The bizarre adventures of the three gunmen Western grosser, next to a delicate young.

programme.desc: Cowboy Movie - A series of reversals bring two desperate people together. When a saloon owner is framed by his partner for a stagecoach robbery, he fights to secure an acquittal.

programme.title: Shoot the Living and Pray for the Dead
programme.desc: After Dan Hogan and his gang rob a bank, they hire a mysterious man to guide them across the Mexican border in return for half of the loot.

programme.title: Robbery Under Arms
programme.desc: Two brothers join their father in Captain Starlights bush ranger gang in 19th Century Australia.

programme.title: A Bullet for the General

programme.title: Fistful of Lead
programme.desc: Sartana contends with various parties - including a dapper rival gunfighter, an alluring saloon owner and a Mexican bandit - who are intent on acquiring a mining directors gold.

programme.title: The Plunderers
programme.desc: Cavalry officer John Drum attempts to track down outlaw Whit Lacey, but finds he must join forces with Lacey to fight a Sioux war party.

programme.title: Heads or Tails

During the trip the two deputies to whom she’s been entrusted rape and leave her in the desert, certain that she’s dead. The girl is found by Black Talisman, an outlaw, who takes her to his hideout, nurses her back to health and after hearing her story, determines to avenge her and clear her name.

programme.title: Mackenzies Raiders EP21-24
programme.desc: Colonel Mackenzie, commander of the 4th Cavalry Regiment at Fort Clark near Brackettville in Kinney County in southwest Texas during the 1870s, receives secret orders from President Ulysses S. Grant and Secretary of War William W. Belknap to stop bandits from crossing the Rio Grande into the United States, or from returning to Mexico.

programme.title: BLITZN
programme.desc: Get ready for a special holiday BLITZ! with master mixologist Yvonne Langen as she prepares her favorite holiday cocktails and party snacks in the Gusto TV kitchen!

programme.title: Flour Power Holiday Specials
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Twists on the Classics
programme.desc: Christmas is right around the corner and it calls for a little fun - like a twist on traditional holiday desserts! FLOUR POWER CHRISTMAS: TWISTS ON THE CLASSICS offers a new take on some of your favourites to bring you a fresh perspective and world of flavour for the holidays! Enchanting host Jessica McGovern plays off classic desserts, serving up handy hints on how to get the most out of every bite. From sweet and fluffy Gumdrop Cakes drizzled with a light lemony glaze to a delectable Eggnog Ski Slope Cake decorated with rosemary trees and a few friends to hit the hills, Jessicas unique holiday recipes will surly make it on your list of Christmas traditions!

programme.title: Christmas With Bonacini
programme.desc: Christmas with Bonacini is a charming one-hour holiday special featuring celebrity chef Michael Bonacini and his son Oscar. Michael inspires with his favourite Christmas recipes that will add a twinkle of sophistication to your dinner table while lifting holiday spirits.

programme.title: Spencers Holiday BBQ
programme.desc: Join charismatic chef Spencer Watts at his glorious rooftop patio for a one-hour special featuring a full holiday spread, all made on the BBQ. Spencer’s festive menu is all about creative BBQ twists with his delectable, mouth-watering recipes including Burnt Orange Cranberry Marmalade, Maple Rye Pumpkin Pie, and Asparagus with Smoked Salmon Dip. Save room for the piece de Q-sistance: Smoked Turkey Two Ways. This year, take your holiday feast outside and serve up something deliciously different.

programme.title: Flour Power Holiday Specials
programme.desc: The holidays are here! And the holidays come with a lineup of treats you wont be able to resist! From sweet and salty to traditional and unconventional, FLOUR POWER CHRISTMAS: BIG WOW DESSERTS covers it all. To get in the holiday spirit, enchanting host Jessica McGovern introduces two desserts that could impress any Scrooge. First, Jessica bakes a decadent Chocolate Yule Log stuffed with a creamy Salted Caramel Frosting and finishes with a holiday-inspired cake decorated with homemade peppermint candy canes! Interwoven with tricks of the trade, Jessica guides us through her simple yet inspiring treats that are perfect for a big Christmas celebration.

programme.title: One World Kitchen Bakes the Holidays
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 One World Kitchen Bakes the Holidays
programme.desc: Celebrate the holidays with One World Kitchens baked treats from Italy, Japan, Thailand, and Argentina. Our hosts Vanessa, Hana, Pailin, and Natalia put a global twist on classic recipes with Panforte, honey-drizzled Struffoli, Matcha Cheesecake, Thai Shortbread Cookies, Turron, and Pan Dulce. Our warm hosts serve up sweet treats inspired by traditions and family secrets. One World Kitchen: Bakes the Holidays will put you in the festive spirit and bring new holiday traditions to your home!

programme.title: Michael Bonacinis Christmas at the Farm
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Michael Bonacinis Christmas at the Farm
programme.desc: In this heartwarming holiday special, Chef Michael Bonacini invites us to his cozy farmhouse in Ontario for a charming Christmas feast. In this scenic winter retreat, Bonacini interprets classic Welsh and Italian Christmas dishes from his childhood. Michael cooks up comforting dishes from hearty potato leek soup, to succulent roast lamb, to classic molten chocolate lava cake. As he explores homey Christmas flavours, Michael shares his traditions and gives tips for perfecting the holiday meal.

programme.title: Watts Up for the Holidays
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Watts Up for the Holidays
programme.desc: Spencer Watts serves up his take on traditional holiday fare, showing us that you can make an impressive dinner without the stress. programme.desc: Christmas is near, and the pressure is on! Between work, home, friends, and family, the list of people to buy for is endless. Fun host Jessica McGovern shows us how to bake something for everyone including Crispy Brittle Bark covered in chocolate, rich Coal Cookies that are sweet with a bit of heat, adorable peanut butter-chocolate Reindeer Cupcakes, and easy-to-make Christmas Puzzle Cookies.

Christmas Sushi Rolls, Veal in a Creamy Tuna Sauce with Capers, Striped Bass in Garlic and Lime Marinade, and an epic Timballo. For the final recipe, our hosts combine all the flavors of One World Kitchen into a truly internationally-inspired turkey dish.

Spencer’s festive menu is all about creative BBQ twists with his delectable, mouth-watering recipes including Burnt Orange Cranberry Marmalade, Maple Rye Pumpkin Pie, and Asparagus with Smoked Salmon Dip. Save room for the piece de Q-sistance: Smoked Turkey Two Ways. This year, take your holiday feast outside and serve up something deliciously different.

programme.title: Flour Power Holiday Specials
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Twists on the Classics
programme.desc: Christmas is right around the corner and it calls for a little fun - like a twist on traditional holiday desserts! FLOUR POWER CHRISTMAS: TWISTS ON THE CLASSICS offers a new take on some of your favourites to bring you a fresh perspective and world of flavour for the holidays! Enchanting host Jessica McGovern plays off classic desserts, serving up handy hints on how to get the most out of every bite. From sweet and fluffy Gumdrop Cakes drizzled with a light lemony glaze to a delectable Eggnog Ski Slope Cake decorated with rosemary trees and a few friends to hit the hills, Jessicas unique holiday recipes will surly make it on your list of Christmas traditions!

programme.title: One World Kitchen Bakes the Holidays
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 One World Kitchen Bakes the Holidays
programme.desc: Celebrate the holidays with One World Kitchens baked treats from Italy, Japan, Thailand, and Argentina. Our hosts Vanessa, Hana, Pailin, and Natalia put a global twist on classic recipes with Panforte, honey-drizzled Struffoli, Matcha Cheesecake, Thai Shortbread Cookies, Turron, and Pan Dulce. Our warm hosts serve up sweet treats inspired by traditions and family secrets. One World Kitchen: Bakes the Holidays will put you in the festive spirit and bring new holiday traditions to your home!

programme.title: Michael Bonacinis Christmas at the Farm
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Michael Bonacinis Christmas at the Farm
programme.desc: In this heartwarming holiday special, Chef Michael Bonacini invites us to his cozy farmhouse in Ontario for a charming Christmas feast. In this scenic winter retreat, Bonacini interprets classic Welsh and Italian Christmas dishes from his childhood. Michael cooks up comforting dishes from hearty potato leek soup, to succulent roast lamb, to classic molten chocolate lava cake. As he explores homey Christmas flavours, Michael shares his traditions and gives tips for perfecting the holiday meal.

programme.title: One World Kitchen
programme.desc: Host Joanna Chery elevates four Greek dishes using wine and spirits in this episode of One World Kitchen. First up, brown rice Stuffed Mussels infused with Greek dry white wine, tangy lemon juice, and fragrant spices - perfect for a sunny day by the sea. When evening rolls around, Joanna insists that red wine is a must! She makes a Sausage and Pepper Stew packed with golden-brown sausages and colourful bell peppers simmered in yummy tomatoes and a healthy dose of red wine. Then, she pulls out some brandy for a tender and delicious Beef Orzo Casserole. Finally, Joanna uses a traditional licorice-flavoured spirit called ouzo to bake a mouth-watering batch of Drunk Cookies.

programme.desc: Jimmy och Darren ar två tennisspelande broder som har glidit isar. Darren ar i pengaknipa och Jimmy jagar svunna tiders framgångar på tennisbanorna och darfor återforenas de for ett minst sagt optimistiskt forsok att kvala in till en Grand Slam-turnering. Båda har sett sina basta dagar, men med hjalp av några okonventionella vanner och en uppmuntrande, men cynisk pappa full av mordande kommentarer kanske de två medelmåttorna kan hitta tillbaka till det som kravs for att vinna over eliten.Med komikerna Jeremy Sisto, Adam Devine och den Oscar® vinnande skådespelaren J.K.

programme.title: Mångalen (Moonstruck)
programme.desc: I denna klassiska romantiska komedi ar en anka från Brooklyn (Cher) redo att gifta om sig. Den har gången planerar hon att gora det ratt, aven om hon måste saga ”ja” till en man hon egentligen inte alskar. Men nar hon blir kar i sin fastmans bror (Nicolas Cage) foljer en romantisk komplikation vardig de storsta komiska operorna! Olympia Dukakis medverkar också.

programme.title: Off the Rails
programme.desc: Nar deras nara van går bort och lamnar tågbiljetter åt dem ger sig tre kvinnor over femtio ivag for att reprisera sin ungdoms europeiska tågluffaraventyr. Vannen har dock en sista onskan: Att de tar hennes tonåriga dotter med sig. Den har gången upplever de att resan genom Europa ar besvarligare an forra gången. Forsvunna pass, tågstrejker och ovantade romantiska forvecklingar satter vanskapen på spel. Frågan ar: Hinner de i tid for att hedra sin vans minne?

programme.title: Date and Switch
programme.desc: Sistaårseleverna Michael och Matty har varit basta kompisar sen lågstadiet. Då de fortfarande ar oskulder sluter de en pakt att hjalpa varandra att få i sang någon innan studentbalen, men deras planer andras drastiskt nar Matt berattar att han ar homosexuell.

programme.title: Låt de doda vila
programme.desc: Jimmy ar inte bara en fan av heavy metal, skrack, och det ockulta. Han har ett mål: han vill kontakta sin avlidna mamma. Den nya killen i klassen, charmoren Amir, lockar Jimmy till att imponera skolans två snyggaste tjejer, Louise och Anna, med en liten rit. Efter riten inser Jimmy, att han har begått ett forfardligt misstag, som kan grava fram doda hemligheter och betyda hela jordens undergång.

programme.title: A Haunted House 2
programme.desc: I denna hysteriskt roliga uppfoljare återvander Marlon Wayans som Malcolm, som efter att ha drivit ut sin exs demoner borjar om på nytt med sin nya flickvan och hennes två barn. Efter att ha flyttat in i deras dromhem plågas Malcolm återigen av bisarra paranormala handelser, och den har gången ar det inte bara huset som ar hemsokt! Jamie Pressly, Cedric the Entertainer och Essence Atkins medverkar också.

programme.title: 7 Days to Vegas
programme.desc: 7 Days to Vegas is an edgy comedy that is based on a true story of the rise and fall of one of Hollywoods biggest poker games. The names have been changed to protect the guilty. Out of desperation to feed his family, Duke Hamilton, a washed up Hollywood actor in the 90s, starts up a small poker game from his house in the lower-class part of the San Fernando Valley. With the help of his wife KC, the game grows to attract some of the biggest players in the Los Angeles area. These risk-taking guys, who will bet on anything, live life on the edge. Its not just Poker that these spoiled LA moguls bet on.

programme.title: A Haunted House
programme.desc: I denna skandalosa parodi på Paranormal Activity-filmerna hemsoks ett ungt par som precis flyttat in i sitt dromhem. Kort efter inflyttning upptacker de att de inte langre ar ensamma. Men det ar inte huset som ar hemsokt, det ar Malcolms flickvan. Malcolm hyr in allt från praster till Ghostbusters så att denna demon inte ska få forstora hans forhållande ... eller, annu viktigare, hans sexliv.

programme.title: Dom kallar mej Trinity - Djavulens hogra hand
programme.desc: Denna vildsinta parodi på ""7 vågade livet"" gjorde Spencer/Hill till stjarnor! Han har en kaft lika valoljad som hans revolver. Han har ett rykte lika smutsigt som kladerna han rider i. Han sager att han ar en fredens man - men vem vågar tro honom? Hans namn ar Trinity - Djavulens hogra hand. I stan traffar Trinity sin ohangde bror Bambino och de kommer i bråk med den skurkaktige Majoren som forsoker ta over stan. Men Trinity och Bambino moter hotet med det enda språk som bovar forstår kulor och storsmockor!

programme.title: Fanboys
programme.desc: En grupp Star Wars-fans reser till Skywalker Ranch for att stjala ett exemplar av ”Det morka hotet”, så att deras dodssjuka van kan se den innan den slapps på bio flera månader senare.

programme.title: I Love You Phillip Morris
programme.desc: Steve Russell (Jim Carrey) ar lyckligt gift med Debbie (Leslie Mann) och en monsterinvånare i staden dar de bor. En bilolycka får honom att drastiskt omvardera sitt liv. Steven inser genom en uppenbarelse att han ar gay och beslutar sig for att leva sitt liv fullt ut, aven om det innefattar att bryta mot lagen. Stevens nya syn på livet gor att han ganska snabbt hamnar i fangelset. Dar tar livet annu en ny vandning och han blir galet kar i Phillip Morris, en kanslosam och lågmald kille (Ewan McGregor). Stevens hangivelse att få leva ett liv i frihet tillsammans med Phillip driver Steve till fler och flera innovativa brott.

programme.title: Death At A Funeral
programme.desc: En komisk vriden historia om en dysfunktionell familj som samlas for att sorja sin patriarks bortgång. Daniels far har just avlidit och det enda han vill ar att genomfora begravningen som planerat, vilket inte ar det lattaste med en galen familj på halsen. Brorsan ar mest intresserad av att ragga tjejer, en annan slakting ar overtygad om att fadern ar vid liv i kistan och en mystisk pillerburk dyker standigt upp. Denna dråpliga komedi i brittisk tradition bjuder på många overraskningar.

programme.title: Middle School: The Worst Years Of My Life
programme.desc: Rafe Khatchadorian har ett efternamn som ar svårt att uttala, hans fantasi ar rent episk och så har han en smula svårt for auktoriteter. Han ar mer engagerad grabb an rebellisk anarkist och ar nu på vag till sin senaste forsta skoldag på sin tredje hogstadieskola. Det ar ett sista chansen-skolbyte som hans hårt arbetande singelmorsa hoppas ska visa sig vara som klippt och skuret for Rafe. Men på Hills Village-skolan satts individualismen i skymundan genom skolans tyranniska uppforandekod.

programme.title: The Birdcage - Lånta Fjadrar
programme.desc: I denna hysteriska komedi har Armand och Albert byggt det perfekta livet for sig sjalva genom att skota sin nattklubb i Miami. Men deras pastellfargade lugn skakas nar Armands son meddelar att han ska gifta sig med dottern till den ultrakonservativa senatorn Keeley... och de ska alla samlas till middag! Kan Armand och Albert forvandla sig till Herr och Fru Familjevarderingar i tid?

programme.title: Hercules I New York
programme.desc: Forvisad från Mount Olympus skickas Hercules, (Arnold Schwarzenegger), till jorden dar han hittar sann karlek och borjar en lovande karriar som kroppsbyggare.

programme.title: Barbershop: The Next Cut
programme.desc: Det har gått mer an 10 år sedan vårt senaste besok på Calvins Barbershop. Calvin och hans trogna team ar fortfarande dar, men butiken har genomgått stora forandringar. Mest markbart ar att vår tidigare mansdominerade fristad nu ar konsblandad.

programme.title: Neighbor for sale
programme.desc: Nick (WILL FERRELL) har en riktigt dålig dag. Forst får han sparken från jobbet som han haft i 16 år. Nar han kommer hem upptacker han sedan att hans fru har kastat ut hans saker på grasmattan, och bytt lås i dorren. Han har forlorat allt. Detta får Nick att overge sin sex månader långa nykterhet och med olen i handen inratta sitt vardagsrum på grasmattan, dar han fordriver tiden med att titta på grannarna. Nar polisen dyker upp for att mota bort honom, hittar han losningen i ett kryphål i lagen: invånarna i Plano i Texas har ratt att hålla privata loppmarknader i fem dagar i strack.

programme.title: Come to Daddy
programme.desc: Nar Norval får ett ovantat brev från sin frånvarande far, reser han till faderns ensligt belagna hus vid havet. Men mycket snart marker han att något kanns valdigt konstigt, och istallet for en efterlangtad familjeåtertraff ar han istallet fast i en helvetisk mardrom.

programme.title: MacGruber
programme.desc: Nar varldsfreden står på spel, nar terroristerna ligger på lur, nar varlden behover en superhjalte med hår som Hillary Clinton... vem kontaktar man då? MacGruber forstås! Enkrigsmaskin utan vapen som kan få ut ALLT av ett gem. En agent så hemlig att inte ensVI kanner till hans fornamn. En man som kvinnor vill vara och som man vill vara tillsammans med... eller ar det tvartom?

programme.title: Fat Kid Rules The World
programme.desc: Troy Billings ar 17 år, overviktig och ska ta livet av sig. Precis nar han ska hoppa ut framfor en buss raddas han av Marcus, en charmig gatumusiker som har hoppat av high school. En skakig vanskap uppstår mellan de två killarna nar Marcus ber den fullstandigt omusikaliske Troy att bli trummis i ett nytt punkband. Troy tror att det hela mest ar på skoj, men i realiteten ar drivfjadern Marcus stora drom om att bli punkrockvarldens kung, med alla medel som kravs..

programme.title: Over the Hill Gang
programme.desc: A retired Texas Ranger and his three aging pals are hired to clean up a lawless town. Starring Walter Brennan, Edgar Buchanan, Andy Devine, Jack Elam, Gypsy Rose Lee, and Rick Nelson.

programme.title: Sagebrush Trail
programme.desc: John Wayne plays a man wrongly convicted of murder in this exciting western drama from Lone Star Pictures. Youll enjoy plenty of gun action and thundering hoofbeats as he escapes from jail and then joins a gang, hoping to find the real killer! Director Armand Schaefer (The Miracle Rider, The Lost Jungle) whips up some fine performances from a cast of B-movie favorites, including Lane Chandler (Samson and Delilah) and the great stunt rider, Yakima Canutt. And of course, the film features plenty of fight scenes, made memorable by John Waynes big swinging right fist! For film buffs: This was one of 11 films Wayne starred in that year, making 1933 one of the busiest years of Waynes...

programme.title: Santa Fe Trail
programme.desc: Oscar winner Michael Curtiz (Casablanca, Mildred Pierce) directed this exciting drama about Army officer Jeb Stuart and the days leading up to the Civil War. Errol Flynn (The Adventures of Robin Hood) stars as Stuart, with Olivia de Havilland as his romantic interest (the seventh of nine times they were paired together by Warner Bros.) The cast includes Ronald Reagan as General George Custer, and Raymond Massey as John Brown, with such familiar faces as Alan Hale and Van Hefflin in supporting roles. Filmed partly in Santa Fe!

programme.title: Doomed Caravan
programme.desc: Hoppy is enlisted to help protect Jane Travers next caravan against robbers who have been terrorizing travelers. He comes across a wily pair of thieves who hve their men disguised as soldiers to escort the caravan. Hoppy isnt fooled for a second and busts up their plan with help from the Bar 20 boys. Not to be outdone, the thieves then capture everyone but Hoppy and puts them before a firing squad. Not its up to Hoppy to rescue his friends singlehandedly. The cast includes William Boyd as Hopalong Cassidy, with Russell Hayden and Andy Clyde as Luky Jenkins and California Jack. For those counting, this was the 32nd of 66 Hopalong Cassidy adventures. They would be edited for syndication...

programme.title: Across the Plains
programme.desc: Savagery! Murder! Renegade white men on the lawless frontier! Two young brothers are separated when their wagon train is attacked and their parents are killed. One brother is raised by Indians. The other falls in with a band of outlaws. Later, the brothers meet up on opposite sides of a battle. Addison Randall, Glenn Strange, and Hal Price star in this rugged tale from Monogram Pictures.

programme.title: Abilene Town
programme.desc: Ablaze with guns and guts and glory! Randolph Scott headlines as a star studded cast in this yarn about battling homesteaders. Director Edwin L. Marin (Tall in the Saddle) spins this dramatic post-Civil War tale that takes place in the legendary cow town of Abilene, Kansas, coaxing fine performances from the likes of Ann Dvorak, Edgar Buchanan, Thonda Fleming, and Lloyd Bridges. Saddle up and hang on!

programme.title: Born to Battle
programme.desc: Cyclone Tom Saunders starts a ruckus in a Chinese laundry and has to go before a judge. Unable to pay his fine, he is bailed out by a local cattle rancher and agrees to do 30 days work for him. Its not too long before he becomes enmeshed in a war between rustlers and outlaws.

programme.title: Call of the Forest
programme.desc: Theres plenty of drama in this tale of lost gold mines, gallant stallions, and fuzzy bears. Starring Ken Curtis, Robert Lowery, and Chief Thundercloud, this charming little film is highlighted by Karl Struss stunning photography

programme.title: Mason of the Mounted
programme.desc: Canadian Mountie Mason is sent south of the border to look for a horse thief with only a watch chain for evidence. He befriends young Andy and when Calhoun hits Andy, Mason and Calhoun fight. In the scuffle Calhouns watch with the missing chain is dislodged. Mason then sets out to bring in Calhoun and his gang.

programme.title: Adventures of Annie Oakley
programme.desc: Sam is framed by Duke and his gang, who have kidnapped Linda to prevent Sam from proving his innocence. Its up to Annie and Lofty to save Sam from an angry mob, save Linda from Duke and his gang, and take them down for their crimes. Annie Oakley: Gail Davis, Deputy Craig: Brad Johnson, Tagg Oakley: Jimmy Hawkins. This western adventure series aired from 1954-1957. Cowboy star Gene Autrey was an executive producer for the show, which was nominated for a Primetime Emmy in 1955.

programme.title: The Hanged Man
programme.desc: After a condemned gunfighter (Steve Forrest) survives his own hanging, he helps a young widow stop a pitiless land baron from taking her ranch. This television feature boasts a strong cast of recognizable characters, including Will Geer, Sharon Acker, Dean Jagger, BarBara Luna, and Cameron Mitchell. Director Michael Caffey would go on to work on such hit shows as Barnaby Jones and MacGyver. Also, look for John Mitchum, younger brother of Robert, in a small role. This movie originally aired on ABC-TV and was considered the pilot for a possible series. Writer/producer Andrew Fenady was behind several opular TV shows such as Branded and The Rebel, as well as the 1970 John Wayne feature, Chisum.

programme.title: Cry Blood Apache (Edited Version)
programme.desc: An Apache brave seeks vengeance on a band of sadistic gold hunters in this bloody drive-in western. Pitcalin (Jody McRae) leads the marauders who wipe out an Apache camp when they discover gold, only to watch their violent deeds lead to their own demise. Featuring a superb cast that also includes Dan Kemp, Robert Tessier, and Joel McRae, this coldblooded western tale was directed by character actor and filmmaker Jack Starrett (Cleopatra Jones, The Losers).

programme.title: The Dawn Rider
programme.desc: John Wayne was still a few years from major stardom when he appeared as John Mason, a man seeking revenge for his fathers murder. Marion Burns stars as Alice, Masons love interest, while Reed Howes stars as Masons friend and rival for Alices affection. When Mason finally tracks down the man responsible for his fathers death, will Ben help, or stand in his way? Produced by Lone Star Pictures, the group behind many of Waynes early films, The Dawn Rider is a stirring yarn about the price of vengeance.

programme.title: The Outlaw
programme.desc: Billy the Kid, Pat Garrett, and Doc Holliday ride again in Howard Hughes epic 1943 western, but the character youll remember most is sultry country vixen Rio McDonald. Hughes nationwide search for an actress to play Rio resulted in the film debut of Jane Russell, whose natural assets were allegedly helped by a special bra designed by Hughes. When The Outlaw finally received a nationwide release in 1946, its success vindicated Hughes and made Russell a star. As for Hughes infamous bra, Russell said in her 1988 memoir, I never wore it, and he never knew.

programme.title: Outpost In Morocco
programme.desc: George Raft, Mary Windsor, and Akim Tamiroff star in this romantic drama from director Robert Florey (The Florentine Dagger, Daughter of Shanghai). Raft plays Capt. Gerard, a member of the Foreign Legion known for his romantic entanglements. Hes assigned to escort an emirs daughter to her fathers mountain citadel and learn about the emirs activities. Not surprisingly, Gerard finds trouble brewing! With footage shot in Morocco, this movie also features a beautiful musical score by twotime Oscar nominee Michel Michelet (Voice in the Wind).

programme.title: The Gunman from Bodie
programme.desc: The Rough Riders, a popular group that thrilled audiences in the early 1940s, are after a gang of rustlers in this B-western from Hollywoods Poverty Row. Starring Buck Jones, Tim McCoy, and Raymond Hatton, this movie features everything from lawmen going undercover to the Rough Riders looking after an orphaned baby! Also, be on the lookout for the beautiful Christine McIntyre, who would go on to appear in several of the Three Stooges shorts for Colombia Pictures.

programme.title: The Red Rope
programme.desc: Hired killers and Old West outlaws stand front and center in this riveting tale from Hollywoods Poverty Row. Bob Steele, one of the busiest stars in movie history (everything from the silent era to Republic Pictures to working with Clint Eastwood in Hang Em High) is here as Tom Shaw, the target of a bad mans desperation and hate. Steele appeared in more than 240 movies and television shows, but was never more impressive than in The Red Rope!

programme.title: The Terror of Tiny Town
programme.desc: Some incredibly small actors were hired to star in this peculiar cult film. Its all about the villainous Bat Haines (Little Billy Rhodes), who is wreaking havoc on Tiny Town. Can Buck Lawson (Billy Curtis) and the townspeople band together and drive him away? This oddity, which was originally distributed by Columbia Pictures, was directed by one of the most prolific low budget filmmakers in Hollywood history, Sam Newfield, a man with over 200 movies to his credit. While it has appeared on many Worst of all time lists, it deserves to be seen at least once!

programme.title: Springtime in the Sierras
programme.desc: Ads for this Roy Rogers classic roared HEAD FOR THE MUSICAL HILLS...ROY IS GUNNIN FOR THRILLS! And thrills are what youll get when you watch this fun, action packed B-Western from Republic Pictures. Theres some great comic relief from Andy Devine and Chester Conklin, two of Hollywoods all-time greats. This old-fashioned shoot-em-up was directed by William Witney, who would go on to direct many of televisions top western sagas, including Bonanza, Wagon Train, and The Wild, Wild West.

programme.title: Cowboy G-Men
programme.desc: Pat Gallagher and his sidekick Stoney Crockett are Secret Service agents in the Old West, dispatched by the government to investigate crimes threatening the young nation. In General Delivery, the G-men crack a government swindle. Starring Russell Hayden, Jackie Coogan

programme.title: Cowboy G-Men
programme.desc: In Gypsy Traders, a band of gypsies settles down in the Montana Territory to take advantage of the copper stakes theyve made in the region. In the nearby town of Bender, a group of shady locals believe the settlers should be stripped of their rights and take the matter to court. When it looks like the judge is going to rule for the gypsies, the outlaws kidnap him and lock him in the local jail.

programme.title: Petticoat Junction
programme.desc: Uncle Joe tries to convince two rich women that Shady Rest is a farm. Uncle Joe Carson: Edgar Buchanan. Betty Jo Bradley: Linda Henning. Kate Bradley: Bea Benaderet. Sam Drucker: Frank Cady. Also starring Pat Woodall and Jeannine Riley. Directed by Guy Scarpitta..Series created by Paul Henning. Episode first aried in February of 1964.

programme.title: Cisco Kid
programme.desc: Cisco and Pancho get swindled by a fake cattle buyer. Starring Duncan Renaldo as The Cisco Kid, and Leo Carillo as Pancho. This weekly adventure series was a favorite of the 1950s, following two pals as they traveled the old west, righting wrongs and helping the underdog. The show was produced by ZIV Television, the same company that gave us Highway Patrol and Sea Hunt, and was nominated for a Primetime Emmy in 1951 This episode aired in 1951.
